slowness in reducing interest rates, we are on hold at the moment. As such,
I would like to propose a hybrid model as the best method for us to create
a long-term relationship during these challenging times. I would like to
take a few steps before I invest in your funds in the following manner:


After setting up an introductory meeting or call and then concluding due
diligence, I enter into an agreement with you, the GP, to help fundraise
for a reasonable monthly retainer, and a success fee. I will agree upon the
signing of the placement agent contract to take a part of the success fee
and invest in the fund as a LP rather than being paid in cash. There is
flexibility to this structure to be cash flow positive for the GP. I like
to do this over at least a 3-fund cycle and envision investing between
$5-10 million during this time, depending on the size of your funds.

If this model conceptually is agreeable to you, I would be glad to confirm
a meeting to discuss it in more detail. Otherwise, we can consider nearer
Q4 2026 for scheduling a zoom call to consider if I would be a passive LP
in the fund.

Please click here to  Schedule a meeting
<https://calendly.com/russell-deakin/30-min-call>

Look forward to hearing from you

Please let me know.
Regards,

Russell







